#. [leadership], id=aoadiscipline
#: .\data\AoA_data\abilities.cfg:7
msgid ""
"Protects friendly units from time-of-day penalties. These units fight as if "
"there was a neutral unit. It also have the same effects as leadership"
msgstr ""

