#: .\data\AoA_data\abilities.cfg:95
msgid "repair +8"
msgstr ""

#. [heals], id=aoaRepair
#: .\data\AoA_data\abilities.cfg:96
msgid "female^repair +8"
msgstr ""

#. [heals], id=aoaRepair
#: .\data\AoA_data\abilities.cfg:97
msgid ""
"Allows the unit to heal adjacent mechanical allied units at the beginning of "
"our turn. A mechanical unit cared for by this healer may heal up to 8 HP per "
"turn."
msgstr ""

#. [resistance], id=AE_aoaRunicResistance
#: .\data\AoA_data\abilities.cfg:114
msgid "runic resistance"
msgstr ""

#. [resistance], id=AE_aoaRunicResistance
#: .\data\AoA_data\abilities.cfg:115
msgid "Gives adjacent allied units 10*level magical resistance to the limit of 50%"
msgstr ""

#. [resistance], id=AE_chs_protection
#: .\data\EoC_data\abilities.cfg:8
msgid "protection"
msgstr ""

#. [resistance], id=AE_chs_protection
#: .\data\EoC_data\abilities.cfg:10
msgid ""
"Adjacent units of lower level from this side receive a +20% bonus to all "
"resistances (up to a maximum of 50%)."
msgstr ""

#. [dummy], id=AE_chs_physical_endurance
#: .\data\EoC_data\abilities.cfg:102
msgid "physical endurance"
msgstr ""

#. [dummy], id=AE_chs_physical_endurance
#: .\data\EoC_data\abilities.cfg:104
msgid ""
"Units with this ability instantly regenerate half of the damage dealt to them"
" unless its type is arcane, or the damage amount would kill them otherwise "
"(greater than or equals their remaining HP)."
msgstr ""

#. [hides], id=AE_chs_camouflage
#: .\data\EoC_data\abilities.cfg:198
msgid "camouflage"
msgstr ""

#. [hides], id=AE_chs_camouflage
#: .\data\EoC_data\abilities.cfg:200
msgid ""
"This unit can hide in deserts and dunes, and remain undetected by its "
"enemies.\n"
"\n"
"Enemy units cannot see this unit while it is in desert or dunes, except if "
"they have units next to it. Any enemy unit that first discovers this unit "
"immediately loses all its remaining movement."
msgstr ""

