"This unit is from the Steelhive faction. Its coding and art were done by "
"Zerovirus and melinath.\n"
"\n"
"These things are so useless. 4 squares of movement per turn on any terrain "
"and 40% defense on any terrain. They can't even attack. At least they have a "
"lot of health and can be used as ZOC dummies.\n"
"\n"
"At least, they require minor maintenances..."
msgstr ""

