"This unit is from the Steelhive faction. Its coding and art were done by "
"Zerovirus and melinath.\n"
"\n"
"Some Slashers, instead of developing two limbs, develop a multitude of limbs "
"in an erratic fashion. While the Steelhive is at a loss to explain these "
"anomalies, that does nothing to prevent them from sending these mutant drones"
" into combat anyways. The robots themselves are quite powerful, combining "
"Swarm and Berserker abilities. While extremely powerful at the beginning of "
"combat, its power gradually lowers as the battle continues and its limbs are "
"removed, one by one, until it is no longer able to fight and is easy to "
"destroy."
msgstr ""

