"This unit is from the Steelhive faction. Its coding and art were done by "
"Zerovirus and melinath.\n"
"\n"
"These units have no combat moves, period. While this makes them seem useless,"
" they are actually nodes in which an extensive matrix of information travels."
" As such, they are responsible for broadcasting commands, making them roughly"
" equivalent to a unit with Leadership. They are almost always protected by a "
"phalanx of drones and are not easy to target. This unit upgrades to a Steel "
"Cybercore if it can survive one battle, gaining 1 XP."
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type], id=AE_agl_steelhive_Cybercore, race=AE_agl_steelhive, gender=female
#: .\units\misc_units\steelhive\cybercore.cfg:3
