"This unit is from the Steelhive faction. Its coding and art were done by "
"Zerovirus and melinath.\n"
"\n"
"When a Cybercone feels that it is threatened by a nearby enemy, it deploys "
"into Core mode. The Core can, like the Steel Choriote, use a Battery Pulse to"
" damage enemies and steal their energy. Its leadership trait is not affected "
"by this change, though, making an attempt to destroy a Cybercone a dangerous "
"proposition."
msgstr ""

