#: .\units\misc_units\steelhive\fideliant.cfg:12
msgid ""
"This unit is from the Steelhive faction. Its coding and art were done by "
"Zerovirus and melinath.\n"
" \n"
"Not as strong as Steel Vorpal in a 1vs1 duel, but once it desides to trample "
"an opponent it will do lethal damage to him, at the cost that fidelant "
"exposes itself in positions in which it can be seriously damaged. It can also"
" choose to impale its victim to, death being a much safer attack but not so "
"deadly. The reflexes of this machine cause that even at close range it may "
"first strike a man with a pike. Additionally, its aerodynamic shape and speed"
