"Once a mandragora has grown, it becomes creepier and unlike mandragora even "
"yokai do not like this much this plants. It's once seen scavening corpses in "
"cementaries, caves and abandoned buildings far from civilization, and unlike "
"the younger mandragoras they will try to chase their prays if hungry enough, "
"all starting with a horrible scream but if comes too close of a living, we "
"just have to assume it most likely become mandragora's next meal."
